@startuml

actor Gost
participant Angular
participant API
participant "Auth Service" as AUTH
participant "Email Service" as EMAIL
database Oracle

Gost -> Angular : Registracija

Angular -> API : POST /register

API -> AUTH : createUser()

AUTH -> Oracle : INSERT uporabnik

Oracle --> AUTH : userId

AUTH -> AUTH : generateVerifyToken()

AUTH -> EMAIL : sendVerificationEmail()

EMAIL --> Gost : Verifikacijski email

Gost -> Angular : Klik na link

Angular -> API : verify-email

API -> Oracle : update verified=true

API --> Gost : Račun potrjen

@enduml